"use strict";(self["webpackChunkwyf2025"]=self["webpackChunkwyf2025"]||[]).push([[594],{1368:function(a,e,t){t.r(e),t.d(e,{default:function(){return c}});var d=t(6768),i=t(4278);const n={id:"div_aboutme",class:"container",style:{display:"block"}};function o(a,e){return(0,d.uX)(),(0,d.CE)("div",n,[...e[0]||(e[0]=[(0,d.Fv)('<div class="photo_containter" data-v-47236d54><img src="'+i+'" alt="me" data-v-47236d54><p data-v-47236d54>Hong Kong University<br data-v-47236d54>Hong Kong<br data-v-47236d54> wangyifanlea@gmail.com </p></div><div class="cv_containter" data-v-47236d54><h2 style="color:#5BA689;font-family:&#39;Arial&#39;,&#39;myfont&#39;;" data-v-47236d54><strong data-v-47236d54>Yifan Wang</strong> ⛵ 汪依凡</h2><p data-v-47236d54><strong data-v-47236d54>Hi! Welcome to my website!</strong> I am a first-year master student in Artificial Intelligence at <a href="https://www.hku.hk/" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>the University of Hong Kong</a>, with a BSc in <a href="https://cs.fudan.edu.cn/main.htm" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Information Security</a> from <a href="https://www.fudan.edu.cn/en/" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Fudan University</a> and a minor in <a href="https://xwxy.fudan.edu.cn/NewsEn/main.htm" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Journalism</a>. My academic background has been shaped by both technical rigor and humanistic reflection, which led me to explore not only how algorithms function, but also what kinds of realities they quietly construct.</p><p data-v-47236d54>My research interest lies at <strong data-v-47236d54>the intersection of AI, data visualization, and computational social science</strong>, especially in how data encodes power, how models influence human perception, and how we might build technological systems that are more human-centered, accountable, and emotionally resonant.</p><p data-v-47236d54>I am guided by the belief that technology is never neutral — it is always connected to histories, institutions, and ways of seeing the world. So while I work with algorithms, I also think about their epistemology, their assumptions, and their implications, in the hope of designing systems that do not merely predict the world, but understand and care for it.</p><p data-v-47236d54>Ultimately, I hope to become a researcher who moves fluidly between engineering and reflection — someone who treats data not just as numbers to optimize, but as stories of people, relations, and possibilities.</p><p data-v-47236d54>Recently, I have been diving into <strong data-v-47236d54>post-training techniques</strong> and <strong data-v-47236d54>agentic AI systems</strong> — exploring how models can be aligned, fine-tuned, and orchestrated to act autonomously in complex environments. I am actively looking for opportunities (internships or research positions) in these areas, where I can contribute to building more capable and responsible AI systems.</p><p data-v-47236d54>Outside of research, I hope to keep thinking, creating, and growing. I enjoy reading, and my current interest lies in communication studies — especially the political economy of communication. I also love learning new languages and new ways of understanding the world; I’ve studied Cantonese, French, and German (thanks, Fudan!). Beyond academia, I am also on my way to becoming a capable independent developer😎😃😃.</p><p style="color:#5BA689;font-weight:bold;" data-v-47236d54>希望我们能够一起在探索世界、认识社会的道路上越走越远！</p><p data-v-47236d54>(thinking how to translate it...)</p></div><div class="news_title" style="display:inline-block;text-align:center;width:20%;color:#5BA689;font-weight:600;font-size:20px;" data-v-47236d54><p data-v-47236d54>News &amp; Travels <br data-v-47236d54>&amp; Awards : )</p></div><div class="news_containter" data-v-47236d54><div data-v-47236d54>01/2026 · Start to be a Tutor in HKU for &quot;[CCAI9010]AI, Communication, and Society&quot;</div><div data-v-47236d54>07/2025 · <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.11841" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Affective GeoVisualization Design</a> is accepted by IEEE VIS 2025.</div><div data-v-47236d54>07/2025 · <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.11903" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Visual Rhetoric of Persuasive Cartography(Octopus)</a> is accepted by IEEE VIS 2025.</div><div data-v-47236d54>06/2025 · ChinaVis Conference, Served as both a conference volunteer and a presenter 📍Hangzhou, China</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2025 · 🏆 Outstanding Gruaduate of Fudan Ubiversity</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2025 · CHI Conference, 📍Yokohama, Japan</div><div data-v-47236d54>04/2025 · IEEE PacificVis, Delivered a presentation 🏆 Best Paper Award</div><div data-v-47236d54>02/2025 · <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2502.04940" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>More Than Beautiful...</a> is accepted by PacificVis 2025.</div><div data-v-47236d54>2024 · 🏆 FDU Graduation Excellent Student Scholarship</div><div data-v-47236d54>2023 · 🏆 FDU Undergraduate Excellent Student Scholarship</div><div data-v-47236d54>2023 · 🏆 Hornorable Mention, Mathematical Contest In Modeling</div><div data-v-47236d54>12/2023 · 🏆 中国国际“互联网+”大学生创新大赛 国家级 铜奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>12/2023 · 🏆 上海是女大学生创新创业大赛“创意组”三等奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>12/2023 · 🏆 五角场创新创业大赛 创业新芽奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>12/2023 · 🏆 “创青春”中国青年创新创业大赛（数字经济专项） 国家级 银奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>11/2023 · 🏆 上海国际创客大赛 创新奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>11/2023 · 🏆 全国大学生数学建模竞赛上海市二等奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>08/2023 · 🏆 第十六届全国大学生信息安全竞赛三等奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>06/2023 · Start to be a TA for “Introduction to Python”, <a href="https://iss.fudan.edu.cn/" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>FISS Program</a> (<a href="https://cse.ucsd.edu/people/faculty-profiles/paul-cao" target="_blank" data-v-47236d54>Paul Cao, USCA</a>)</div><div data-v-47236d54>04/2023 · 🎾😎 Tennis Umpire, FDU Interdepartmental Tennis Cup (复旦院系网球赛)</div><div data-v-47236d54>01/2023 · 🏆 第十四届全国大学生数学竞赛（非数学类）三等奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>11/2022 · 🏆 全国大学生数学建模竞赛上海市二等奖</div><div data-v-47236d54>2021 · 🏆 FDU Undergraduate Excellent Student Scholarship</div><div data-v-47236d54>2021 · 🏆 &quot;Advanced Individual&quot; of Tengfei College, FDU</div><div data-v-47236d54>2021 · 🏆 复旦大学信息学院优秀共青团员</div><div data-v-47236d54>2021 · 🏆 复旦大学书院之星提名奖（团体）</div><div data-v-47236d54>10/2021 · 🎾😎 Tennis Umpire, FDU Open Tennis Tournament (复旦网球公开赛)</div><div data-v-47236d54>10/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance, 📍SJTU(XUHUI)</div><div data-v-47236d54>10/2021 · 🎵 Vocal Recording for Peking Opera “The Great Tang Concubine”（大唐贵妃） Background Music</div><div data-v-47236d54>07/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance(First time acting training from a musical actor!!), 📍Music in the Summer Air (MISA,上海夏季音乐节)</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · Shot Put &amp; Sit-up Athlete, FDU Sports Meet</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · 🏓 Mixed Doubles Player, FDU Table Tennis Open &amp; College Cup(复旦乒乓球公开赛&amp;书院杯)</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · Start my interest in VIS~~~ </div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance, 📍SHANGHAI INTERNATIONAL DANCE CENTER上海国际舞蹈中心</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance, 📍SHANGYIN OPERA HOUSE上音歌剧院</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance, 📍FDU</div><div data-v-47236d54>05/2021 · 🎵 FDU Choir Performance, MV Recording</div><div data-v-47236d54>12/2020 · 🎵 129 Choir Competition, FDU Choir Performance, 📍相辉堂</div><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.2;color:#5BA689;" data-v-47236d54>When I write this section, I often wonder: <br data-v-47236d54>who am I beyond my awards? <br data-v-47236d54>These are only a small part of me, so I decided to include some other experiences as well.</p></div>',4)])])}var r=t(1241);const s={},v=(0,r.A)(s,[["render",o],["__scopeId","data-v-47236d54"]]);var c=v},4278:function(a,e,t){a.exports=t.p+"img/me2.f51af91c.png"}}]);
